<lyrics>[V1]
 Rili cung khualtlawn caan a dih, Kan inn dawh bik kan naih cang, Rili
 cung khualtlawn caan a dih, Kan inn dawh ah kan phan lai.

[C1]
   Thlichia hrangmi a dai zau lai, lawng dinhnak nuam ah kan phan lai,
   Rili cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai, Rili
   cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai.

[V2]
 Mi tampi cu him in an phan, Khi sui ti kam dawh ahcun, Mi tampi cu
 lamtim an phan, Siseh hmun tampi a um.

[C2]
   Thlichia hrangmi a dai zau lai, lawng dinhnak nuam ah kan phan lai,
   Rili cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai, Rili
   cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai.

[V3]
 Thlizil hrang ah lawng hri samh hna, Kan lawng cu hmaiah kal seh,
 Lawng cung um lawmhnak hla an sa, Tlanhnak tling hla dawh bik cu.

[C3]
   Thlichia hrangmi a dai zau lai, lawng dinhnak nuam ah kan phan lai,
   Rili cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai, Rili
   cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai.

[V4]
 Him tein tikam ah kan hren, Harnak cu kan lonhg dih cang, Khuapi dawh
 ah kan leng hna lai, Zungzal hla kan sa ti lai.

[C4]
   Thlichia hrangmi a dai zau lai, lawng dinhnak nuam ah kan phan lai,
   Rili cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai, Rili
   cung khualtlawn caan a dih in, Kan inn dawh cu kan phan lai.</lyrics>
